			Note
		
		&lt;/span&gt;
	&lt;/div&gt;
	&lt;div class="alert-body"&gt;
		&lt;p&gt;We don&amp;rsquo;t need generated &lt;code&gt;archetypes&lt;/code&gt;, &lt;code&gt;assets&lt;/code&gt;, &lt;code&gt;i18n&lt;/code&gt;, &lt;code&gt;layouts&lt;/code&gt; folders in the &lt;code&gt;newsite&lt;/code&gt; folder&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Foundation</title><link>https://dumindu.github.io/E25DX/docs/foundation/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://dumindu.github.io/E25DX/docs/foundation/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="install-hugo"&gt;Install Hugo&lt;/h2&gt;
